Summary: very small starlike object travelling just before dark
divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting on the bench in my garden and looked to my right and saw a very small light in the sky travelling. I thought it was much to small to be a plane. I have seen so many strange things in the sky over my house and surrounding area I am rarely without my camera anymore so I took some photos and video of the object. I wasnt able to get much before my view was totally obscured as it moved further away. attached are 3 short videos. I'm not sure what this was but I have had Many sightings of unexplainable objects in the last three years. I really believe I might live in some sort of "hotspot".
